    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. The 6 non-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 4. Validation evidence demonstrates MARE of 8.3% against in-vitro hemolysis measurements. Relative hemolysis index RH < 1 at all 5 operating points (range 0.61–0.88). An extensive UQ campaign documented in the validation report confirmed robustness of the hemolysis predictions across the geometric tolerance space. The model is deemed credible for the stated COU: identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device.",
